dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents future land use for Eau Claire County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, EauClaire_Future_LandUse_2017.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'FarmlandPreservation', 'GoldenTriangle_AEA', 'Groundwater_Protection_District', and 'Zoning'.
